replies.body:
Thanks! It means a lot to me! :D

Yes, Syndra is definitely not in the right state of mind to help anyone right now, but I trust she'll grow, eventually... At least that's what I'm getting from the Seer's prophecy in The Dreaming Pool!

Unless by turn back you meant, geographically, since she's headed North and Wuju is down South...? {{sticker:slayer-jinx-wink}}
